column4: <content>Massacre of Innocents. Not by P.B.I, though some pentimenti in horse legs and to [the] right of [the] woman with little girl standing on the right by the willow tree. Bottom right corner on a piece of wood: BRVEG (rest covered by frame). Complete photo of right bottom corner needed. Tree trunks very poor, not the wealth of irregular 'painterly scratches' as e.g. in Bird Nester.</content>
